TIPS TO KEEP IN MIND for AD Quality:
*Quality ranking depends:
1-Clickbait nhi lgane 
2- ye nhi kehna comment 'yes' i will post phuspha 2 movie (engagemet bait)
3-aise words nhi use krne jo possible na ho jese world's best smartphone (ad copy) and pixles ache ho (ad creative)
4- dont say inbox me
6-dont target same people so they might get irriatated and result in hiding/not interested posts(high frequency rate min:1,max:2)

*Engagement ranking depends:
1- relevenacy .e.g targeting male for selling bra while female wear it
2-ad copy (bara titie nhi hon, comment kro, jhoot nhi likhna)
3- engament creative be creative

*Converstion rate:
1-targeting/releavncy
2-landing page

