Events and pixel:
1-Online events:
100 people landed on page+80 clicked on product(viewed content)+50 added to cart + 30 checkout+ 10 bought
then we create custom audeince pf 50 people who added to cart and retarget them,their lookalike audienece too. 10 people
 who bought we retarget+lookalike audience(ask fb to find similar people who bought)
2-offline events:
guy landed on page but didnt buy instead called/went to physical store pixel didnt detect because he didnt buy so we give fb his mail/data and ask them to find 
retarget andf lookalike aduience
3-custom events:
clicked on refund/size then we retarget them and give satisfaction of rewfund and size etc
4-custom conversion:
pixel doesnt tell us that 100 people bought 100rs produict and 50 people bought 1000rs product so we ask facebook to create custom audeince of 1000rs people 
buying product and retarget/look alike audience


