if one guy bought product so only product event triggers not all 4(althogh he passed all of them) and if he added to cart then only this triggers not view products.

standard optimization:
fb finds less purchase like 300rs kay paisay hamse legi aur 300 ki purchase lakr degi agr 600 ki purchase ajaye to pixel direction tabdeel krdegi aur less purschas 
wo bhi less budget pr
